        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Secure Embassy Construction and Counterterrorism Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill modifies various requirements pertaining to the security of U.S. diplomatic facilities. For example, each U.S. diplomatic mission must have an emergency action plan that addresses a range of threats. Currently, the plan is only required by statute to address the threat of large explosive attacks from vehicles. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
